      <section eId="sec_265_08">
        <num>265.08</num>
        <heading>Criminal use of a firearm in the second degree</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_265_08__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision one of section 70.02 and he either:\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_265_08__subsec_b__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>possesses a deadly weapon, if the weapon is a loaded weapon from\nwhich a shot, readily capable of producing death or other serious injury\nmay be discharged; or\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_265_08__subsec_b__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>displays what appears to be a pistol, revolver, rifle, shotgun,\nmachine gun or other firearm.\n  Criminal use of a firearm in the second degree is a class C felony.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
